highlights.text: Taylor Swift has the most spots on Top Songs USA. “Cruel Summer” is the highest at #5.
“No Role Modelz” by J. Cole has been on Top Songs USA the longest, at 165 weeks straight.
“Like Crazy” by Jimin is the biggest gainer on Top Songs USA, up 102 spots at #70.
“Seven (feat. Latto)” by Jung Kook and Latto is the highest new entry on Top Songs USA at #3.
